string.text: I rushed to the market early today after work to buy some fresh ingredients to bring home

string.name: Txt603
string.text: It's a rare occasion when I have time to surprise him by cooking a nice dinner

string.name: Txt604
string.text: I carried a heavy basket of vegetables to the doorstep of my house

string.name: Txt605
string.text: There seemed to be two figures

string.name: Txt606
string.text: With confusion, I walked into the house

string.name: Txt608
string.text: My home is repaired, so it's a little easier

string.name: Txt609
string.text: I have a roof over my head, but I still have to find a way to make ends meet.

string.name: Txt610
string.text: I still had to find a job to make a living, otherwise what would I do with the baby?

string.name: Txt611
string.text: A job... Damn, I've been divorced for so long and I don't even have a job.

string.name: Txt612
string.text: Let me think about what I can do for a while.

string.name: Txt613
string.text: The sun is pouring through the window.

string.name: Txt614
string.text: I was flicking through the morning paper when a prominent job posting caught my eye

string.name: Txt615
string.text: "The restaurant is looking for a restaurant manager, good pay, apply!"

string.name: Txt618
string.text: Hello, I'm here to apply for the position of restaurant manager

string.name: Txt619
string.text: Welcome, I'm the head chef of this restaurant, let me see what you've got

string.name: Txt620
string.text: That's great! you've impressed me and I'd love to hire you as restaurant manager

string.name: Txt621
string.text: Thank you for your confidence, I'd love to take the job

string.name: Txt622
string.text: That's great, we'll work together and we'll make the restaurant better and better!

string.name: Txt623
string.text: I have been working in the restaurant for a few months now and I have found the head chef to be a very nice person

string.name: Txt624
string.text: I would love to share my experiences and thoughts with him

string.name: Txt626
string.text: You know, when I first came here, I had no one to turn to and life was hard with a child

string.name: Txt627
string.text: Yes, it's good that you're finally getting better now

string.name: Txt628
string.text: Yes, our restaurant business has gotten better in the past few months

string.name: Txt629
string.text: I finally got a new house and I can start a new life.

string.name: Txt630
string.text: This is great. Can I help you with anything?

string.name: Txt631
string.text: It would be great if you could help me with the renovations.

string.name: Txt632
string.text: I'm willing to help in any way I can, so let's do it together

string.name: Txt633
string.text: Thank you, you're a very nice person

string.name: Txt634
string.text: You're welcome, we all have something to appreciate

string.text: Lucas and I smiled at each other and a new plan began to emerge
